{"tid":1092603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：「問候689」籌款爆額 吳文遠︰梁實在太乞人憎 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-04-05T03:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T04:10:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d66ac30575f0bd76bc159ff522d5477ac389bb7f","tid":1092603,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190405/20649592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F20649592&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=3c175736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F20649592&h=d7f1faa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190405/20649592</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：「問候689」籌款爆額<br />\n吳文遠︰梁實在太乞人憎 - 李八方<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190405/large/a1305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190405%2Flarge%2Fa1305a.gif&h=7931dc8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大將軍現身公民黨慶，即時被該黨領導層捉住合照。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n近日689喺fb日日數《蘋果》全版廣告當向北京交功課，引起關心689嘅網民同KOL熱烈討論，齊齊玩夾錢登廣告「深切問候」，當中社民連主席吳文遠火速籌款達標，周一將喺《蘋果》頭版賣廣告問候689，文遠大將軍噚日有去公民黨黨慶，大將軍一現身即時被該黨領導層捉住合照，笑佢因為同689做筆友，已經成為「大紅人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190405/large/1554396018_99d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554396018_99d9.jpg&h=b31370e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n籌得16萬元 料可再登一次內頁<br />\n<br />\n文遠大將軍話噚日下畫已就籌款截咗數，共籌得16萬元，遠超預期嘅12萬，所以佢相信周一賣完頭版廣告後，仲可以賣多次內頁廣告。對於巿民今次捐款反應熱烈，文遠大將軍解釋時都忍唔住笑，話自己只諗到一個原因：「就係梁振英實在係太乞人憎嘞！」<br />\n<br />\n大將軍又搞笑話，今次大家籌款反應熱烈，令佢都有少少妒忌，因為社民連過去籌款打官司，啲巿民反應都未有咁踴躍，但佢都明白香港巿民今次係為咗出啖氣，令689唔好咁得戚。對於廣告內容，佢話因為擔心最鍾意告人嘅689會再出律師信，所以佢已同三個律師及《蘋果》法律部嘅同事溝通咗兩日，希望收到好消息，呼籲大家只要周一買份《蘋果》睇吓，就會知道有乜精采內容嘞！  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：公民黨慶Tanya判刑前唱《夢伴》「剩下我北風中漆黑中帶着淚」 (李八方)"},{"pid":"92b2b011f00ed74f6c77c43cf44ef10b2f2d91d0","tid":1092603,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"問候689<br />\n得不到分數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5aed22d2e05e6f564c4d4feea89b5851f0eb184","tid":1092603,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a407fa57f009f33c8dd55b5761810e9258d6a194","tid":1092603,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"星期一"},{"pid":"367fb8df8b464969173c09102e647d943783c2e2","tid":1092603,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:08:42.000Z","msg":"吳文遠食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"7a19c3c9a0dad1fc3131d70dac81b99a0e07588d","tid":1092603,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}